asked that question...

1265
01:14:41.343 --> 01:14:44.471
I'd like to jump in and take that one.
Jimmy. if you don't mind.

1266
01:14:45.914 --> 01:14:47.973
Have at it. hoss.

1267
01:14:48.050 --> 01:14:49.984
