1287
01:16:12.434 --> 01:16:15.335
B. Pythagorean triplets?

1288
01:16:15.404 --> 01:16:19.568
<i>Or C. the migration method of graphing</i>
<i>quadratic functions?</i>

1289
01:16:22.578 --> 01:16:24.546
Harriot's method of solving cubics.

1290
01:16:24.613 --> 01:16:27.605
<i>The answer is A. Harriot's method</i>
<i>of solving cubics.</i>

1291
01:16:33.922 --> 01:16:35.549
