<i>at Dean Pritchard's former residence.</i>

1443
01:26:46.567 --> 01:26:49.161
<i>You all remember that crazy bastard.</i>

1444
01:26:50.537 --> 01:26:53.768
<i>We'd love for you to join us</i>
<i>this Saturday at our open house</i>

1445
01:26:53.841 --> 01:26:57.868
<i>for some chips. soda.</i>
<i>and some late</i>- <i>night streaking.</i>

1446
01:26:57.945 --> 01:27:00.436
Little right. Little more.

1447
01:27:00.981 --> 01:27:03.108
Yeah. that's good enough.
That's good enough.

1448
01:27:03.717 --> 01:27:05.844
- Welcome aboard. Booker.
- Thank you. sir.

1449
01:27:05.919 --> 01:27:08.353
- Walsh. Well done.
- Frank the Tank.

1450
01:27:08.422 --> 01:27:10.287
Why don't you get me
a fresh beer?

1451
01:27:10.357 --> 01:27:11.551
You serious?

1452
01:27:11.625 --> 01:27:12.751
Now!

1453
01:27:13.127 --> 01:27:16.426
Now! Hurry. you sorry son-of-a-bitch!

1454
01:27:18.632 --> 01:27:21.931
* <i>Going down the only road</i>
<i>I've ever known</i>

1455
01:27:23.670 --> 01:27:27.538
* <i>Like a drifter I was born</i>
<i>To walk alone</i>

1456
01:27:30.144 --> 01:27:32.635
* <i>And I've made up my mind</i>

1457
01:27:46.026 --> 01:27:48.654
Aahh!

1458
01:27:50.664 --> 01:27:51.961
Oh. shit.

1459
01:28:03.177 --> 01:28:07.341
* <i>I close my eyes</i>

1460
01:28:07.414 --> 01:28:12.442
* <i>Only for a moment</i>
<i>And the moment's gone</i>

1461
01:28:13.287 --> 01:28:17.280
* <i>All my dreams</i>

1462
01:28:17.958 --> 01:28:22.122
* <i>Pass before my eyes</i>
<i>A curiosity</i>

1463
01:28:22.830 --> 01:28:27.199
* <i>Dust in the wind</i>

1464
01:28:27.267 --> 01:28:30.964
* <i>All we are is</i>
<i>Dust in the wind</i>

1465
01:28:31.271 --> 01:28:33.205
Stay in the goal.

1466
01:28:33.273 --> 01:28:35.707
We gotta stay in the goal.
You can't be walking around.

1467
01:28:35.776 --> 01:28:38.040
You're killing me.
Can we stay between the posts?

1468
01:28:38.111 --> 01:28:41.638
I want focus. I want intensity.
and I want "1.2.3"!

1469
01:28:41.715 --> 01:28:42.841
Woofers!

1470
01:28:42.916 --> 01:28:46.818
Go. go. go. eat 'em up!
Hungry! Eat 'em up!

1471
01:28:46.887 --> 01:28:50.983
Caleb. you know what to do in the box.
We talked about it. in the box!

1472
01:28:51.058 --> 01:28:53.026
Chill out. we're up by six.

1473
01:28:53.093 --> 01:28:57.826
That ref's a real prick out there.
That's right. you heard me. my man!

1474
01:28:57.898 --> 01:29:01.698
Number four's been throwing elbows.
and someone's kid's gonna get hurt.

1475
01:29:01.768 --> 01:29:03.167
What?

1476
01:29:03.237 --> 01:29:05.068
Let's make it official then. jackass!

1477
01:29:05.138 --> 01:29:06.901
Let's make it official!

1478
01:29:07.774 --> 01:29:10.800
Get the clipboard.
I'll be in the car. all right?

1479
01:29:10.878 --> 01:29:12.937
- Have some respect for yourself.
- Thank you.

1480
01:29:13.680 --> 01:29:16.649
Is that Frank the Tank?

1481
01:29:16.717 --> 01:29:18.810
Hey. Heidi.

1482
01:29:19.686 --> 01:29:22.621
- How you doing?
- I'm doing really good.

1483
01:29:22.689 --> 01:29:25.522
I got into body painting.

1484
01:29:25.592 --> 01:29:27.423
- I didn't know that.
- Yeah.

1485
01:29:27.494 --> 01:29:28.586
That's great.

1486
01:29:28.662 --> 01:29:31.324
Well. you're looking
very healthy.

1487
01:29:31.398 --> 01:29:34.697
Oh. thanks.
Yeah. so are you.

1488
01:29:34.768 --> 01:29:36.702
Oh. thank you.

1489
01:29:36.770 --> 01:29:40.137
So. I heard you and Marissa
split up. Is that true?

1490
01:29:40.207 --> 01:29:42.072
Yeah. we did.

1491
01:29:42.809 --> 01:29:44.743
You poor baby.

1492
01:29:45.546 --> 01:29:47.104
You know. I'm having
this get-together

1493
01:29:47.180 --> 01:29:48.772
at my place
tomorrow night.

1494
01:29:48.949 --> 01:29:52.680
Like a few Internet friends.
You should swing by.

1495
01:29:52.753 --> 01:29:54.744
- Really?
- Totally.

1496
01:29:55.589 --> 01:29:57.022
- Okay.
- All right.

1497
01:29:57.090 --> 01:30:00.253
- That sounds awesome.
- See you tomorrow night.

1498
01:30:03.096 --> 01:30:04.427
Awesome.

1499
01:30:04.498 --> 01:30:05.931
Yes!

1500
01:30:08.835 --> 01:30:10.700
I am back!

1501
01:30:15.000 --> 01:30:20.000
Ripped by
..::McLane::..
